  body: I would love to see Matrix eat its own dog food and thread messages with timestamps and search filters. Live chat tech support is privileged to the IRC few. The reasons are immense to make it a reasonable request to have live help a part of research, and it would be a real distinct feature for Matrix as a greater support tool.
